    ________                                   \e[1;31mONLY FOR EDUCATIONAL PURPOSES.\e[1;32m
   / ____/ /_  ____ _____  ____ ____  _____
  / /   / __ \/ __ `/ __ \/ __ `/ _ \/ ___/                          
 / /___/ / / / /_/ / / / / /_/ /  __/ /       \e[1;37mCreated by "Micro-sys/Mac_changer"      \e[1;32m   
 \____/_/ /_/\__,_/_/ /_/\__, /\___/_/  v1       
                        /____/    
\e[1;33m
\e[1;36m Your Mac address = '$wlan0' \e[1;33m

1. Lenovo Laptops       11. Samsung Laptops  
2. Hp Laptops           12. Nokia Laptops           
3. Asus Laptops		13. Vaio Laptops               
4. Msi Laptops      	14. Micromax Laptops
5. Apple Laptops        15. HCL Laptops           
6. Acer Laptops         16. Wipro Laptops	21. Castom Mac Address
7. Dell Laptops         17. LG Laptops		22. MY ACCOUNTS - CONTACT WITH ME
8. Microsoft Laptops    18. Reliance Laptops	23. EXIT
9. Huawei Laptops       19. Sony Laptops                   
10. Xiaomi Laptops      20. Gateway Laptops
'
