    __  ___         
   /  |/  /___ ______      
  / /|_/ / __ `/ ___/ 
 / /  / / /_/ / /__  
/_/  /_/\__,_/\___/  
                                          
    ________                                  
   / ____/ /_  ____ _____  ____ ____  _____
  / /   / __ \/ __ `/ __ \/ __ `/ _ \/ ___/   
 / /___/ / / / /_/ / / / / /_/ /  __/ /               
 \____/_/ /_/\__,_/_/ /_/\__, /\___/_/  v1.  
                        /____/         (Linux)   
 \e[1;32m
 https://github.com/Micro-sys/Mac_Changer
 \e[1;37m
 sahinm808@gmail.com
              Press ENTER to Main Menu
'

read

